CHILDREN:
Golden Pacific will accept for transportation, without charge, not more than
one child under two (2) years of age, who does not occupy a separate seat and
is accompanied by a passenger paying the full fare.
Children under two (2)
years of age, occupying a seat, or over two (2) years of age and less than 12
years of age, will be charged 66⅔% of the adult fare when accompanied by an
adult passenger paying the adult fare. Individuals twelve (12) years of age and
over will be charged the full adult fare.
BAGGAGE ALLOWANCE:
3 pieces, 1st - 62",
2nd - 55", 3rd - 45" (measurements are the sum of the
outside linear measurements: length + width + heigth, and must not exceed
the total amount indicated).
Maximum weight: 70 Ibs/ piece.
Excess pieces:
$5.00 each, excess weight: 20¢ a Ib., space available
CHECK IN:
Passengers without tickets please check in 30 minutes prior to scheduled
departure.
Passengers with tickets please check in 15 minutes prior to
scheduled departure.
Reservations not claimed 10 minutes prior to schedule
flight departure are subject to cancellation.
